sac.graphviz

Interface Graphvizable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    GameState, GraphState, State
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Checkers, GameStateImpl, GraphStateImpl, HelloWorldGameState, HelloWorldGraphState, NimState, PackingState, PackingStateFullCuts, SlidingPuzzle, StateImpl, Sudoku, TravelingSalesmanProblem

    public interface Graphvizable
    An interface allowing states to be visualized (as parts of whole graphs or trees) via Graphviz software (http://www.graphviz.org).
    Author:
    Przemysław Klęsk (wi.zut.edu.pl), Marcin Korzeń (wi.zut.edu.pl)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String toGraphvizLabel()
      Returns a representation of a state (pure string or HTML) for Graphviz visualization.
